WEBVTT

00:10:28.505 --> 00:10:36.773
trying to hybrid all 
those different genres,

00:10:36.773 --> 00:10:40.060
trying to regain a certain complexity.

00:10:41.485 --> 00:10:44.000
Why do we record?

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:46.681
I was still there.

00:10:46.681 --> 00:10:50.494
I really believe cinema teaches us to see.

00:10:50.494 --> 00:10:51.900
The way we show the world

00:10:51.900 --> 00:10:56.150
is going to change the 
way we see this world,

00:10:56.150 --> 00:10:58.290
and we live in a moment where the mass media

00:10:58.290 --> 00:11:00.899
are doing a terrible, terrible job